1. *Kraju* smo stigli usred noći. (We arrived at the end in the middle of the night.)
2. U *kraju* smo otkrili neverovatna mesta. (We discovered incredible places in the end.)
3. U *kraju* nam je otkrilo sebe. (In the end, it revealed itself to us.)
4. U *kraju*, hvala Bogu, uspeli smo. (In the end, thankfully, we succeeded.)
5. Ovo je *kraj* naše putovanje. (This is the end of our journey.)
6. Bio je to *kraj* njenog strpljenja. (That was the end of her patience.)
7. *Krajem* meseca ćemo završiti posao. (We will finish the job by the end of the month.)
8. U *kraju* ćemo naći rešenje. (We will find a solution in the end.)